{"type": "article", "id": 62560, "title": "HAY 推出新灯具，玩的是灯臂和灯源的平衡｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-03-31T22:50:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48893, "name": "Sé"}, {"id": 57610, "name": "Vondom"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 54969, "name": "Janne Schimmel"}, {"id": 54968, "name": "Moreno Schweikle"}, {"id": 48896, "name": "Ini Archibong"}, {"id": 8754, "name": "Eugeni Quitllet"}, {"id": 57611, "name": "Sam Weller"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190331222141yCdbFYq4phaOWkIz.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 16.2px Times; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>FIFTY-FIFTY by Sam Weller</h3><p>FIFTY-FIFTY 是一款多功能作业灯系列，包含两种尺寸的台灯与一款落地灯。最初的理念是想将台式工作灯回归到其最为根本的元素。这盏灯基于一个平衡体系，滑锤施加了一个反向的力量，使灯臂和灯源达到平衡。</p><p>FIFTY-FIFTY 的命名来源于使这盏灯两部分达到平衡的平衡体系，由此可以清晰地看到设计师 Sam Weller 对物理和工程学的参考很大程度上影响着其设计。</p><p>可配置的铝制部件简化了设计和生产过程的整体复杂性，创造出一个关节的特征，贯穿于全系列产品中。悬臂很容易用一只手倾斜与转动，还有一个触碰感应式的按钮可以精准定位与控制光源明暗。该系列包含大号和小号两种带底座的台灯和一款落地灯，适用于家中的共享空间或私人空间，或是工作环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222256Vh6CJqKxdcl0rtvz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222256u7eP1NYKaFEAfh0T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312222577sW0nqPyIcCbd5Fl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.207500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222258lONk3CKHZTEudRUa.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222258hvjGZDqAp2XnfuaR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Beaver Glassware Collection by Nendo</h3><p>Beaver 系列是日本设计工作室 Nendo 专门为捷克水晶玻璃制造商 Lasvit 设计的一组六件套玻璃器皿，包括葡萄酒杯、平底玻璃杯、威士忌酒杯、玻璃瓶、长笛玻璃杯、迷你酒杯。</p><p>常规的玻璃器皿制作模式是将杯颈和杯子基座粘结到玻璃底上，Beaver 的设计方法与常规模式截然不同，杯子仿佛是一棵即将倒下的树木，形成了一种紧迫感。拥有随机切割纹路的玻璃杯产生复杂的光线反射，闪烁着水晶所特有的微光。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222346w6GvnVUb0Prc4h5y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222346pRQBMEmCJSYo2b7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222346GJvYKsgEhfo4HalI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222346M7es4KaoISBd0qxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222347fivAkcKBpJMlaVwX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222347gC5Y3wvpybVGZXnc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222347y4mbnWhfj6KMPLUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222347DxNu1KAI2csE0Qlb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222348aHwNoIpmGbx67YSg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222348kocpHusUAOmxSKLB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222348bE4Qr1lxDogH9XOM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312223483T7Yub6QX5eBHzny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Brooklyn Collection by Eugeni Quitllet for Vondom</h3><p>受雕塑艺术以及当代考古学的影响，加泰罗尼亚设计师 Eugeni Quitllet 的项目主要是极具视觉感的骨架型作品。</p><p>他为 Vondom 品牌设计的 Brooklyn 系列座椅与坐凳展现出品牌注重动态并充满激情的潮流的特征。</p><p>Eugeni Quitllet 此次设计的 Brooklyn 系列家具有着永不过时的特征，其外形灵感和名字均来源于纽约最具代表性的布鲁克林大桥。座椅采用注射聚丙烯与玻璃纤维材质制作，其笔直的线条逐渐延伸，形成有机的曲线形态，这种设计也从侧面反映出座椅的舒适性。座椅总高度 83 厘米，目前有带扶手和无扶手两款，还有白色、黑色、土色和淡褐色可供选择。</p><p>与可堆叠座椅相似，Brooklyn 系列坐凳也有两种版本：66 厘米高的坐凳和 76 厘米高的高脚凳。坐凳高挺笔直的凳腿向上延伸，共同支撑起上方圆形的座面。凳腿构成的拱形之间形成一定空隙，创造出亦空亦满的感觉。坐凳设计同样有多个配色可供选择，具体包括红色、青铜色、芥末黄色以及蓝色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222457u5tOdE8KSa1LAs9G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222457UaZzS9qLXc4KfB68.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222459V0zqe9YjnXF1ml6b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222459eDg7dqM0O3pwX1kj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312224595yQimxOqNHvXaAPB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222459kOh9PlriVJUoA0QF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222459ZsEB4dhkiVcmvCjH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312225002N75rBj0OCeMU9kS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222500jseSKOfi4DwhAFTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654034\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://eugeniquitllet.com/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eugeni Quitllet</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Monolithic Furniture Series by Ini Archibong for&nbsp; Sé</h3><p>今年米兰设计周期间，家具品牌 Sé 即将推出 Monolithic 系列的第二部分，出自尼日利亚裔美国设计师 Ini Archibong 之手，据称其灵感来自于天地之间永恒的相互作用，受到立石的整体形状的启发。</p><p>新系列包括照明、玻璃器皿、座椅和桌子，以及更新的木饰面和定制的水晶颜色。</p><p>流线型的 Oshun 沙发以 Yoruba 神灵的名字命名，沙发采用织物和皮革制成，底座由黄铜制成，它可用作沙发或沙发床。另有一款宝座般的 Atlas 桌椅采用实心橡木制成，灵感来自立石，手工染色。Circe 沙发设计适合在室内和室外使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222805O2z3hItSRV8rivsw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615665\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222805jhBTIC0Rmn6dZEOg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312228056iClNAhOkUfyn2b7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222806YeZPpHCukDhzW3RU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://se-collections.com/about/news/collectioniv-partii/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sé</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The CrossFit furniture collection by Janne Schimmel and Moreno Schweikle</h3><p>荷兰 - 德国设计二人组 Janne Schimmel 和 Moreno Schweikle 推出 CrossFit 家具系列，将数字操纵的物体变成真正的家具。</p><p>CrossFit 系列中的两把椅子将典型的简约家具设计与有机形状相结合，将它们“变形”结合在一起，创造出新的形式。每件作品都是数字建模实验的结果。</p><p>“假毛皮允许我们隐藏硬元素和软元素之间的连接点，使它们像在 3D 建模软件中一样毫不费力地融入彼此。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222938zKEYGvFTZer06cDa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222939tTUkRu1OCsj9V04A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903312229394MLFGwEROUW5ZSil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222939167oZfF5QH9cwsbU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222940KZNmjzX8kQUMGTba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222940iGTBzblnewqU5dVc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562788\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190331222940lD8obRB2ZhU4J7LE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/03/29/crossfit-schimmel-schweikle-furniture-collectible/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"medium-insert-active\"><br></p>"}